title: Nichols records No. 3 NCAA mark on day two - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Nichols records No. 3 NCAA mark on day two - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – The Texas Tech track and field team wrapped up day two with impressive performances coming from the field events, highlighted by Monae' recording the No. 3 all-time NCAA mark in the long jump.
